# Claude Code Adapter

This project uses Vibe Paper.

## Working scope

- Read the whole experiment project root.
- Use `paper/context/project_snapshot.md` as the first paper-writing context file.
- Write LaTeX, bibliography, and figure-support files inside `paper/`.

## Expectations

- Preserve claims and numbers from actual project files.
- Prefer structured metrics from JSON, CSV, logs, and exported result summaries.
- Do not invent missing experiments.
- Use the local Vibe Paper build flow when compilation is required.
- If the user wants preview, prefer the native popup script entrypoint instead of an editor-integrated preview.
